name: United Express CRJ-700 Night Takeoff From Vancouver
description:
This is a United Express Bombardier CRJ-700 taking off from Vancouver International Airport (CYVR/YVR) from the inside late at night. Sorry for any fuzzy parts, my camera isn't the best for night videos... Anyway, enjoy the video, and please subscribe!
